title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is placed inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: To reproduce the issue: 1. Create a grid. 2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells. 3. Insert another table into another grid cell.
SR: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when attempting to export data from a table inside a grid cell. Please follow the steps provided in the 'EB' section to reproduce the issue.
